snippet.title: 10 Academy
snippet.description:
10 Academy identifies, trains and enables exceptionally talented young Africans to have an outsized impact on the world.

10 Academy’s vision is thousands of exceptionally talented Africans making social contributions that can go onto impact millions of people in Africa and the rest of the world.

10 Academy provides unique value to trainees in 6 areas:

    Connections – jobs for top performers
    Curated Content – All trainees can access high quality content that has been vetted by experts
    Community – Fellow trainees , experts and tutors create a community.
    Certification – Completion of the course leads to a certificate and a portfolio of results
    Completeness – Course provides the complete range of skills needed for a real data science job
    Cost – Training is free.
